color_gaussian = function(mu,s1,s2){
  return(function(x){
    test =as.numeric(x < mu)
    return(sqrt(2*pi)*(test*s1*dnorm(x,mu,s1) + (1-test)*s2*dnorm(x,mu,s2)))
  })
}

  xyz_fun = function(){
      xyz_par = list(
        x.a = c(1.056,0.362,-0.065),
        x.mu = c(599.8,442.0,501.1),
        x.s1 = c(37.9,16.0,20.4),
        x.s2 = c(31.0,26.7,26.2),
        
        y.a = c(0.821,0.286),
        y.mu = c(568.8,530.9),
        y.s1 = c(46.9,16.3),
        y.s2 = c(40.5,31.1),
        
        z.a = c(1.217,0.681),
        z.mu = c(437.0,459.0),
        z.s1 = c(11.8,26.0),
        z.s2 = c(36.0,13.8)
      )
  
  xfun = function(x){
    xyz_par$x.a[1] * color_gaussian(xyz_par$x.mu[1],xyz_par$x.s1[1],xyz_par$x.s2[1])(x) +
      xyz_par$x.a[2] * color_gaussian(xyz_par$x.mu[2],xyz_par$x.s1[2],xyz_par$x.s2[2])(x) +
      xyz_par$x.a[3] * color_gaussian(xyz_par$x.mu[3],xyz_par$x.s1[3],xyz_par$x.s2[3])(x)
  }
  
  
  yfun = function(x){
    xyz_par$y.a[1] * color_gaussian(xyz_par$y.mu[1],xyz_par$y.s1[1],xyz_par$y.s2[1])(x) +
      xyz_par$y.a[2] * color_gaussian(xyz_par$y.mu[2],xyz_par$y.s1[2],xyz_par$y.s2[2])(x)
  }
  
  zfun = function(x){
    xyz_par$z.a[1] * color_gaussian(xyz_par$z.mu[1],xyz_par$z.s1[1],xyz_par$z.s2[1])(x) +
      xyz_par$z.a[2] * color_gaussian(xyz_par$z.mu[2],xyz_par$z.s1[2],xyz_par$z.s2[2])(x)
  }
  return(list(xfun = xfun, yfun = yfun, zfun=zfun))
}

# the matrix convert rgb to xyz and xyz to rgb xyz = rgb %*% t(rgb2xyz)
rgb2xyz = matrix(c(0.49,0.17697,0,0.31,0.8124,0.01,0.2,0.01063,0.99),nrow = 3)#/0.17697
xyz2rgb = solve(rgb2xyz)

  rgb_na = function(r,g,b){
    k = length(r)
    ind = r<1|r<0|g>1|g<0|b>1|b<0
    cind = seq(1,k)[!ind]
    q = rep("#000000",k)
    q[cind] = rgb(r[cind],g[cind],b[cind],maxColorValue= 1)
    return(q)
  }
  
  xyz2hex = function(x,y,z){
    xyz = as.matrix(data.frame(x,y,z))
    rgb = convertColor(xyz,from = "XYZ",to="CIE RGB") 
    #hsv = rgb2hsv(rgb[,1],rgb[,2],rgb[,3],maxColorValue = 1) %>% t()
    rgb.max = apply(rgb,1,max)
    rgb.max = ifelse(rgb.max == 0,1,rgb.max)
    q = rgb(rgb[,1]/rgb.max,rgb[,2]/rgb.max,rgb[,3]/rgb.max)
  }

xyz_from_lambda = function(lambda){

  df = data.frame(lambda = lambda,
                  x = xyz_fun()$xfun(lambda),
                  y = xyz_fun()$yfun(lambda),
                  z = xyz_fun()$zfun(lambda))
  df = df %>% mutate(X = x/(x+y+z),Y = y/(x+y+z))
  
  xyz = df %>% select(x,y,z)
  rgb = as.matrix(xyz) %*% t(xyz2rgb) %>% data.frame()
  names(rgb) = c("r","g","b")
  df = cbind(df,rgb)
  
  rgb = convertColor(xyz,from = "XYZ",to="CIE RGB") %>% data.frame()
  names(rgb) = c("r2","g2","b2")
  df = cbind(df,rgb)
  
  df = df%>%mutate(q = xyz2hex(x,y,z),q2 = rgb_na(r,g,b))
  
  return(df)
}

rgb2data = function(rgb.mat){
  xyz.mat = convertColor(rgb.mat,from = "CIE RGB", to="XYZ")
  #rgb2xyz = matrix(c(0.49,0.17697,0,0.31,0.8124,0.01,0.2,0.01063,0.99),nrow = 3)
  #xyz.mat = as.matrix(rgb.mat) %*% t(rgb2xyz)
  xyz.mat = as.data.frame(xyz.mat)
  names(xyz.mat) = c("x","y","z")

#the rgb.max operation set the V=1 in HSV
data = xyz.mat %>%mutate(X = x/(x+y+z),Y = y/(x+y+z),rgb.max = 0) %>% 
  cbind(rgb.mat) %>% 
  mutate(rgb.max = ifelse(r>rgb.max,r,rgb.max)) %>%
  mutate(rgb.max = ifelse(g>rgb.max,g,rgb.max)) %>%
  mutate(rgb.max = ifelse(b>rgb.max,b,rgb.max)) %>%
  mutate(rgb.max = ifelse(rgb.max == 0, 1,rgb.max))%>%
  mutate(q = rgb(r/rgb.max,g/rgb.max,b/rgb.max,maxColorValue = 1))
  return(data)
}

#illuminants

plank.weight = function(lambda,Tp){
  m = 10^16*lambda^(-5)/(exp(1.4388e7/Tp/lambda)-1) 
  #take c1 = 10^16, 2*pi*h*c^2 = 3.74177185 × 10-16 m4 kg / s3
  #c2 = h*c/k = 0.014388 m·K
  return(m)
}
illuminant.A.weight = function(lambda,Tp = 2855.54){
  #a = (560/lambda)^5
  #b = (exp(1.4388e7/Tp/560)-1)/(exp(1.4388e7/Tp/lambda)-1)
  #s = a*b
  s = plank.weight(lambda,Tp)/plank.weight(560,Tp)
  return(s)
}

illuminant.D.XY = function(Tp = 6504){
  coef.x.low = c(0.244063,0.09911,2.9678,-4.6070)
  coef.x.high = c(0.237040,0.24748,1.9018,-2.0064)
  ths.l = c(4000,7000)
  ths.h = c(7000,25000)
  coef.y = c(-0.275,2.870,-3)
  tt = 1000/Tp
  if(Tp<=7000){
    coef.x = coef.x.low
  }else{
    coef.x = coef.x.high
  }
  x =sum(tt^seq(0,3)*coef.x)
  y =sum( x^seq(0,2)*coef.y)
  return(data.frame(Tp = Tp, X = x, Y = y))
}
